➜美媒：已有52名叙利亚雇佣兵在纳卡地区丧生
http://www.sohu.com/a/424818365_115376	19815
<div id="sohuplayer">
<script type="text/javascript" src="//tv.sohu.com/upload/swf/showVrsPlayer.js"></script>
